textfsm_template:
Value SEQ (\d+)
Value TTL (\d+)
Value TIME (\d+\.\d+)
Value TRANSMITTED (\d+)
Value RECEIVED (\d+)
Value PERCENT (\d+)
Value TIME_TOTAL (\d+)
Value MIN (\d+\.\d+)
Value AVG (\d+\.\d+)
Value MAX (\d+\.\d+)
Value MDEV (\d+\.\d+)

Start
  ^PING\s+\S+\s+\(\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+\)\s+\d+\(\d+\)\s+bytes\s+of\s+data\.$$
  ^\d+\s+bytes\s+from\s+\S+:\s+icmp_seq=${SEQ}\s+ttl=${TTL}\s+time=${TIME}\s+ms$$ -> Record
  ^---\s+\S+\s+ping\s+statistics\s+---$$
  ^${TRANSMITTED}\s+packets\s+transmitted,\s+${RECEIVED}\s+received,\s+${PERCENT}%\s+packet\s+loss,\s+time\s+${TIME_TOTAL}ms$$
  ^rtt\s+min/avg/max/mdev\s+=\s+${MIN}/${AVG}/${MAX}/${MDEV}\s+ms$$
